=head1 FOR DEVELOPERS

If you are interested in altering the public version of this module,
please note that the distributed files are not the source code of the
module. If you wish to obtain the source code repository of [%
config.base %], please access [% config.repository %] using the "git"
source control system.

The original files of this distribution make heavy use of the
L<Template> Perl module in order to cut down the amount of repetitive
stuff which needs to be put into various source and documentation
files.

